snippet.title: AMBER HEARD WINS - THIS IS WHY Amber Heard Won't Be Removed From Aquaman 2 | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
THIS IS WHY Amber Heard Won't Be Removed From ‘Aquaman 2’ | Celebrity Craze

The situation with Amber Heard in regards to her very public battle against ex-husband Johnny Depp has led many in the public eye to turn against her. Mainly because in the beginning she was ‘very clearly’  via her statements. 

But then, things started to change when Johnny Depps started to provide evidence that she was the, repeatedly in fact. And as more information comes out people want Heard to be punished, including her losing her role as Mera in Aquaman 2.

Did Amber Heard just get booted for Aquaman 2? This would be great news to Johnny Depp and Aquaman fans around the world. The #FireAmberHeard movement is going strong. The Johnny Depp Amber Heard legal battle is still at the forefront of celebrity news. 

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnny #Aquaman2
